\id 2TH - Mupun NT 
\h 2 Tasoloni 
\toc3 2Tas 
\toc2 2 Tasoloni 
\toc1 Lepran Ɗevǝl Ɗe Pool Ran Nenyil Tasolonǝ Mo 
\mt2 Lepran Ɗevǝl Ɗe Pool Ran 
\mt1 Nen Tasolonǝ mo 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Lepran ɗesǝ nǝ put a nsar Pool kǝ Silas, kǝ Timoti. Muu tok kǝ nenɗǝm ndang Naan ɗe mon nTasoloni, ɗe mo a mǝ Naan puun fun kǝ Jesu Kristi. 
\p  
\v 2 Naan puun fun kǝ Daa Jesu Kristi mo shín ɗeret nwun kǝ tongryang zak. 
\s1 Naan nTokɗyeel nGurum Mo a Shi Jesu 
\p  
\v 3 Ɗyemnaa mo, nǝ a tǝng kǝ mu pǝlang Naan mɓe wun shidaar-shidaar. Nǝ ret kǝ mun, mu pǝlang wun aasǝ zak, mbǝɗe cinzeen fuu nǝ nkaa wurang hakyeng, kǝzak, wal fuu mbǝ niyee fuu mo nii seet ɓuɓul ɗak.  
\v 4 A nǝ le ɗang mun shikáa fun muu canpwoo shi wun nenɗǝm ndang Naan mo, mbǝ gung fuu, kǝ shinzeen fuu, kaaɗe wuu ɗar ɗi ɓalɓal jir kǝ ɗe wuu gung kǝ shinjeel kǝ shwaajeel ɗe wuu shwaa mo shini-shini. 
\p  
\v 5 Mbǝ mbii ɗe wuu shwaajeel nǝ mo yaksǝ, parmee puus ɓe mon nkat wun kǝ kwoop nǝ mbǝ mulki Naan. Ɗesǝ mo ɗee a langtǝng mɓe kám nwun nee,  
\v 6 Naan a ngucanɗyeel ɗen ndǝre ndǝre. Mbǝmǝnǝ, wur nshìnjeel nen ɗe mo shínjeel nwun.  
\v 7 Wur nshìn nookɗi nwun kǝ mun jir nɗǝǝn jeel ɗe muu shwaa mo yaksǝ. Mbii ɗesǝ mon nɗen aasǝ parɗe Daa fun Jesu wur ntong nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan sham. Wur nkámkáa fin ashak kǝ nenlep nwur ɗeɓal mo.  
\v 8 Wur njì shi wus ɗe nii bǝlempee, mbǝkǝ wur kwat nen ɗe mo cii Naan ɗe, kǝ nen ɗe mo ciipwoo ɗeret nkaa Daa fun Jesu Kristi.  
\v 9 Kwat mo nǝn nɗee a muut ɗel dǝm kǝ mo ngaa-ngaa. Baa mon mmak naa yit Naan koo ɗeɗes mǝ iiko nwur kas, koo le.  
\v 10 Katɗang wur njì, parpuus ɗeɗes mǝnǝ, ɓe nen nwur mo jir, mon nshin ɗeɗes nwur. Jir nen ɗe mo shinzeen nwur, ɓe mon nkwoop wur, kǝ wun zak wun nɗee nɗǝǝn nen ɗe mon nkwoop wur, mbǝɗe wuu ten wu shinzeen mpwoo wur ɗe mun kǝ sat nǝ nwun. 
\p  
\v 11 Mbǝmǝnǝ ɓe muu ɗangnaan (Leshap kǝ Naan) mɓe wun shidaar-shidaar, mbǝkǝ Naan wur le kǝ wu ɗee ɗekoop nǝ, mɓe zeen ɗe Naan wur pǝrep wun mbǝmǝnǝ. Naan wur le kǝ wu mak cìn koo a mbii ɗeret ɗeɗangyi ɗe wuu pan cìn nǝ mɓe shinzeen fuu shiɓal nwur.  
\v 12 A nɗǝǝn kaan kǝ ar ɗesǝ, ɓe gurum mon nle ram nsǝm Daa Jesu nɗǝǝn wun, kǝ wun ɗe nɗǝǝn wur zak, shi ɗeret Daa Naan fun kǝ Daa Jesu Kristi. 
\c 2  
\s1 Ngwe Ɗebish 
\p  
\v 1 Pwoo nkaa ji nDaa fun Jesu Kristi, kǝ kuur fun pee wur ɗe. Ɗyemnaa mo, mu ɗang pǝ wun,  
\v 2 taji pan fuu mo ɗee a ɗecicǝǝr koo nǝ daampee nwun kas. Mbǝɗe pak gurum moo sat nee, puus Daa nii ten ji. Koo ɗe gurum mo sat pwoo mǝnǝ a nɗǝǝn Riin, nnǝ puus nii ten ɗel, koo a shi liispwoo nǝ, mo aasǝ. Koo kaaɗe pak mo nkaa sat nǝ, nǝ di mu ran pwoo nwun, nkaa nǝ aasǝ nɗǝǝn pwoo ɗe di mu ran nwun sǝ.  
\v 3 Taji wu le kǝ mee gurum ngwam wun kas, koo le. Baa puus nǝ kǝ waaji kas, atǝng nnaar ɗe gurum mon ncíi tuwap kǝ mo cii Naan, nǝn nshee dì akuɗang, kǝ gwar ɗebish, ɗewur ɗee a ɗelǝloom, ɗe mon nvwet wur nɗǝǝn wus, wu njì put agaak akuɗang zak.  
\v 4 Wun ncìn lek nkaa mbii ɗe gurum mo kǝ seyil mmo jir, kǝ wur nlekáa fin a kaa Naan sǝ. A wur nsat nee, wuɗi met mmo jir, kǝzak wur nɗel nɗǝǝn Lu Naan ɗeɗes, kǝ wur ntong a peetong, ɗangɓe wur leshin a Naan. 
\p  
\v 5 Baa wu pan kas aa? kaaɗe gyet mun ashak kǝ wun sǝ, ɓe wen kǝn ten nsat nwun nee, mbii ɗesǝ mo jir mon nɗen aasǝ.  
\v 6 Yaksǝ ɓe, a mee mbii kǝ yaa wur baa kǝnǝ. Wun shikáa fuu, wu man mbii mǝnǝ. Katpee nǝ wul, ɓe gwar ɗebish wur njì put agaak.  
\v 7 Jurum kǝ ɓal kǝ ngwar ɗebish nǝ nkaa cìn ɗak yaksǝ nɗǝǝn yil ɗesǝ nǝ. Ɗangɓe mee ngwar kǝ yaa wu baa kǝ nǝ mɓe reppee ɗeɓen ɗak. Katɗang mo mang ngwar ɗe nii yaa wur baa kǝnǝ,  
\v 8 ɓe ngwar ɗebish nǝ wur njì put. Dangɓe Daa Jesu wur ntu ngwar ɗebish nǝ shi nook kǝ pwoo fin. Katɗang Daa Jesu wur mbaajì nɗǝǝn ɗeɗes fin.  
\v 9 Katɗang ngwar ɗebish wur njì put, ɓe wur njì a nɗǝǝn ɓal mǝ ngunjwaan. Wun ngwam gurum mo shi mbii aapwoo mo ɗes ɗewur ncìn mo.  
\v 10 Wur ncìn ɗak kǝ koo mbii ɗebish ɗeɗangyi, mbǝkǝ wu ngwam nenyil ɗe mon nloom ɗe. Nen ɗesǝ mo ɗee a ɗelǝloom mbǝɗe di mo cii shinzeen, kǝ mo cii wal nzeen. Mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe baa mo kat ɓam kas.  
\v 11 Aasǝ ɓe, Naan cǝǝr kǝ pan fur mo, mbǝkǝ mo shinzeen ɗe a mbii ɗǝ nǝ a ɗung ɓejee ɗak.  
\v 12 Mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe mon nɗee a ɗelǝloom, mbǝɗe mo cii shinzeen atǝng mo kǝlǝng shang mǝ cìn shikbish ɗak. 
\s1 Naan wur bǝlǝp wun 
\p  
\v 13 Ɗyemnaa fun mo, Daa wu wal nwun. Mbǝmǝnǝ ɓe nǝ ret kǝ mu pǝlang Naan mɓe wun. Naan wur ten bǝlǝp wun, pǝgyet ɗi nshee, mbǝkǝ wur kat ɓam wur ɗe nɗǝǝn ɓal Riin fin ɗeɓang, ɗewur le wu ɗee a nen fin ɗeɓang mo shi shinzeen nɗǝǝn mbii ɗe nǝ azeen-nzeen.  
\v 14 Naan wu pǝrep wun, mbǝkǝ wu tong ɗe ashak kǝ Daa Jesu nɗǝǝn ram fin, mɓe pwoo ɗeret ɗe mun kǝ sat nǝ nwun.  
\v 15 Mbǝmǝnǝ ɗyemnaa mo, wu ɗar ɓalɓal, kǝ wu yaa mbii ɗe gyet mu kám mo ɗe, koo ɗe gyet mǝ sat a shipwoo, kǝ koo ɗe gyet mu sat a shi lepran ɗe gyet mǝ ran mo nwun zak.  
\v 16 Daa fun Jesu Kristi shikáa nwur, kǝ Naan puun fun moo ɓam pǝtuup fuu mo.  
\v 17 Kǝ wur shínɓal nwun, mbǝkǝ wur cìn koo a ɗak ɗeɗangyi, kǝ pwoo ɗeret ɗe wuu sat zak. 
\c 3  
\s1 Wu Ɗangnaan (Leshap kǝ Naan) mBǝ Mun 
\p  
\v 1 Ɗyemnaa fun mo, pwoo ɗe muu rǝɓet sat mǝ kyes nǝ a nee, muu ɗang pǝ wun, mbǝkǝ wu ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan) ɗe mbǝ mun. Mbǝkǝ pwoo Naan nǝ kaatpee mo ɗe, kǝ mbǝkǝ gurum mo lap nǝ ɗi kǝkoop, kaaɗe gyet wun wu lap nǝ sǝ.  
\v 2 Kǝzak, wu cìn ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan) mɓe mun, mbǝkǝ Naan wur ɓam mun ɗe nɗǝǝn sar kǝ nen bish mo, ɗe pǝtuup fur mo a ɗe ɗeet. Baa a gurum mo jir, mo shinzeen mpwoo nǝ kas. 
\p  
\v 3 Dangɓe Daa wur kǝ ɗar nkaa zeen. Wur nshin ɓal nwun kǝ wur tap fwang wun aku nsar ngujwaan.  
\v 4 Mu shinzeen nDaa ɓe wun, nǝ, wu cìn mbii ɗe mu sat mo ɗe, kǝ wuu sekyeen kǝ cìn mo zak.  
\v 5 Daa wur nle kǝ wu man wal Naan ɗeɗes mɓe wun, kǝ gung kaaɗe Daa Jesu gung sǝ zak. 
\s1 Taji Wu Ɗee a Seer Mo Kas 
\p  
\v 6 Ɗyemnaa mo, nɗǝǝn sǝm kǝ Daa Jesu Kristi, muu sat nwun shiɓal nee, taji wu ɓalkaa kǝ ɗyemnǝǝn fun ɗe mo a seer mo kas. Shii kǝ mǝnǝ, a nen ɗe baa moo mwaan nkaa kám ɗe gyet mu kám nwun kas.  
\v 7 Wun shikáa fuu, wu man nee, nǝ ret kǝ wu mwaan nɗǝǝn shiimwaan fun, mbǝɗe gyet mun ashak kǝ wun, ɓe baa gyet muu tong kǝ sar fun mo nfii kas,  
\v 8 kǝ baa muu se mbiise nsar mee ngwar zuum kas, amma muu cìn ɗak shiɓal kǝ sar fun mo mpar kǝ puus, mbǝkǝ taji mu lejeel mmee ngwar nɗǝǝn wun kas.  
\v 9 Gyet mun kǝ iiko mbǝkǝ mǝ sat nwun nnǝ wu shin mbiise mmun, ɗangɓe baa gyet mu tal pǝ wun kas, mɓeɗi gyet mu rǝɓet kám nwun ar ɗe wun ncìn ɗak shi sar fuu mo.  
\v 10 Kaaɗe gyet mun ɗe ashak kǝ wun, ɓe muu naa nsatpwoo nwun shiɓal nǝ, katɗang baa mee gurum cìn ɗak kas, ɓe taji wu shín mee mbii nwur se kas.  
\v 11 Mu kǝlǝng nee, pak mo nɗǝǝn wun, moo ɗee a seer mo. Nnǝ baa moo cìn mee ɗak kas, amma nnǝ, moo ɗee mwaan buu, mbǝkǝ mo lep pwoo ɗe nɗǝǝn ɗak kǝ gurum mo.  
\v 12 nƊǝǝn sǝm kǝ Daa Jesu Kristi, muu satpwoo shiɓal nee, nǝ ret kǝ nen mǝnǝ mo nook mwaan mǝnǝ, mbǝkǝ mo cìn ɗak, ɗe mon nkat mbiise mukáa fur mo ɗi, mbǝ pwoo fur mo.  
\v 13 Ɗyemnaa mo, taji kwak fuu mo murǝp mbǝ cìn ɗak ɗeret kas. 
\p  
\v 14 Katɗang mee ngwar cii cìn mbii ɗe mu sat nɗǝǝn pwoo ɗesǝ, ɓe wu naa gwar mǝnǝ rǝret. Taji wu cìn mee mbii ashak kǝ wun kas, mbǝkǝ naashweep yaa gwar mǝnǝ ɗi.  
\v 15 Ɗangɓe taji wu naa wur a kaa shaarlek sǝ kas, ɗangɓe wu fwang wur kaa ɗyemnǝǝn sǝ. 
\s1 Pwoo Mǝ Kyes Nǝ 
\p  
\v 16 Daa Jesu shikáa fin, ɗe ryang kǝ put a pee wur ɗi, wur shìn tongryang nwun nɗǝǝn mbii mo jir. Daa Jesu tong ashak kǝ wun jir. 
\p  
\v 17 Ɗesǝ a sar ran mǝnǝ Pool, ɗe an kǝn le nǝ nɗǝǝn pwoo ɗe moo put pee ghan ɗi. Wen kǝn ran aasǝ.  
\v 18 Ɗeret kǝ Daa fun Jesu Kristi nǝ tong ashak kǝ wun jir. Nǝ aasǝ.